name: Henry
headline: Automating Deal Decks for Commercial Real Estate Brokers
description: Henry is an AI copilot for commercial real estate (CRE) brokers that seamlessly integrates a brokerage’s internal data set with external sources to generate custom presentations and financial modeling for deals. Our mission is to help CRE brokers close more deals faster, earning more while doing less repetitive work. We’re initially focusing on enabling brokers to generate deal decks in seconds—a task that typically consumes 20+ hours a week across multiple departments within a brokerage.
tags: industry:generative-ai; industry:saas; industry:real-estate; industry:ai; industry:ai-assistant; location:new-york

founders.name: Sammy Greenwall, Founder, CEO
founders.description: Sammy is the Co-Founder and CEO of Henry, Co-Founder and former CRO of Lev (which he scaled 0 to Series B / $10M+ run rate), and a retired real estate finance professional. Sammy was born and raised in the Bay Area and played college basketball at Swarthmore College. Sammy is passionate about building great products in large and stubborn markets.

founders.name: Adam Pratt, Founder
founders.description:
2x Founder, Currently CTO and Co-Founder @ Henry.

Previously, Firefighter (Hamilton, NY - Station 19) and Co-Founder @ Halligan (Fire Department Saas Platform). Aquired by Vector Solutions in 2019

# Smarter, Better, Faster Deals.
### Unmatched Speed
Nobody wants to wait weeks for deal decks. With Henry, you don’t have to. Our AI-powered platform gets it done in hours, so you can bring deals to market faster and stay ahead of the competition. We eliminate bottlenecks, so you can focus on closing deals and driving results.
Research doesn’t have to be a grind. Henry’s AI pulls from public data, proprietary intel, and your firm’s own research—processing way more than any single analyst could handle. We turn those insights into accurate, compelling materials you can trust to back your deals.
### High- Quality Research
Elevate your brand with polished, professional materials that build credibility and trust. Henry takes on the functions of graphic designers and marketing teams, delivering sleek deal decks with unmatched attention to detail.

generated_description:
**Company Overview: Henry**

**Mission:** Automating Deal Decks for Commercial Real Estate Brokers

Founded in 2024 and based in New York, Henry is an innovative AI copilot designed specifically for commercial real estate (CRE) brokers. It emerged from the Y Combinator Batch S24, where it honed its vision of simplifying the preparation of deal decks—a task that can notoriously consume over 20 hours a week. By seamlessly integrating a brokerage’s internal datasets with external sources, Henry empowers brokers to create customized presentations and financial models in seconds.

**Why It Matters:** The commercial real estate landscape is competitive, and every minute counts. Henry’s automation capabilities don't just save time; they help brokers close deals more efficiently, enhancing their productivity while significantly reducing the repetitive workload. 

**Current Offerings:**
- **Speedy Deal Deck Generation:** Henry can prepare deal decks in mere hours, positioning brokers to go to market faster than ever.
- **AI-Powered Insights:** The platform utilizes a blend of public data, proprietary intelligence, and the brokerage’s own research to produce comprehensive materials that are both accurate and compelling.
- **Polished Professionalism:** It functions as both a graphic designer and marketing resource, ensuring high-quality, professional presentations that build trust and credibility.

**Team & Structure:** Currently, Henry operates with a compact team of three, led by seasoned entrepreneurs under the guidance of David Lieb, a Group Partner at Y Combinator. This lean approach allows for agile decision-making and rapid evolution of their product.

**Tagline:** Smarter, Better, Faster Deals.

**Key Focus Areas:**
- Generative AI
- SaaS (Software as a Service)
- Real Estate
- AI Assistance

In a space where time is money, Henry is poised to revolutionize the way CRE brokers operate, allowing them to shift focus from tedious administrative tasks to what truly matters: closing deals.

For more information, explore their website at [Henry.ai](http://www.henry.ai).
